          <div class="js-pillar-accent red"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-pillar">
          <div class="js-pillar-num">Pillar III</div>
          <div class="js-pillar-name">Holistic Care</div>
          <div class="js-pillar-desc">Mental health support, family care coordination, meal trains, housing stability, and the full network of community love — before, during, and after trial.</div>
