        <div class="js-pillar">
          <div class="js-pillar-num">Pillar IV</div>
          <div class="js-pillar-name">Protection</div>
          <div class="js-pillar-desc">Coordinated response to harassment, doxxing, and threats against families and their legal advocates. No one stands alone.</div>
          <div class="js-pillar-accent white"></div>
