          <div class="js-how-card-name">Courthouse Witness</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">We organize coordinated, peaceful, lawful presence in the gallery during trial. Travel coordination, lodging, daily witness rotations. We fill the room.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Court Support</div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-how-card">
          <div class="js-how-card-num">02</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-name">Emergency Bail Fund</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">When bond is set at a level designed to imprison rather than ensure appearance, we mobilize. Direct financial assistance. Bond reduction advocacy. Attorney referrals.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Bail Relief</div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-how-card">
          <div class="js-how-card-num">03</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-name">Jail Support</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">For those who remain incarcerated pretrial: commissary, correspondence, family communication, mental health resources, and regular check-ins. No one disappears.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Incarceration Support</div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-how-card">
          <div class="js-how-card-num">04</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-name">Family Care</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">Meal coordination, childcare networks, housing stability support, financial relief for families who have lost a provider to pretrial detention. Whole-family care.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Holistic Support</div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-how-card">
          <div class="js-how-card-num">05</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-name">Legal Network</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">Warm referrals to civil rights attorneys, public defenders, and pro bono legal advocates. We do not practice law — we connect families to those who do.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Legal Advocacy</div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-how-card">
          <div class="js-how-card-num">06</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-name">Protection Protocol</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-desc">Coordinated response to doxxing, harassment, and death threats targeting families and advocates. Documentation, safety planning, and community shield formation.</div>
          <div class="js-how-card-tag">Protection</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

